metadata.name: Lazy Kitties #511
metadata.description:
Welcome to the Lazy Kitties Society!

Be the guardian of these cute kitties born in the Tezos blockchain space.
And please be a part of our Lazy Kitties Society!
https://discord.gg/lazykitties

Let's create a wonderful world with kittens! MEOW!

[Mouse Movement]: Eye Control
[Press 'c' or 'C'] : Kitten's Favorite Cushion (Toggle)
[Press 's' or 'S'] : Save Snapshot (With BG)

metadata.name: Bauhaus art #orange #9
metadata.description:
My orange collection is a Bauhaus style idol
I have designed this collection in 6 layers
The first 4 layers of designs and the combination of lines and shapes
The 5th layer of the cover and the last layer of the frame and noise

The orange and dark blue green colors in this work of art are trying to express themselves and they are fighting each other for this

metadata.name: Introspection #11
metadata.description:
Sketches of geometric shapes with scale symmetry.

"What does the mirror see when it looks in the mirror?"

--

- Live renderer best viewed in Chrome.
- Press "S" to export a standard resolution image.
- Press "P" to export an hi-res image.
- Press "G" to toggle the grain.

metadata.name: Boxes #34
metadata.description:
Boxes are the title of this project. 
But these boxes have a soul, like a society that is 
complete together. In different colors and shapes.
Made in javascript & p5.js
It may take time to load.
Press "s" to download a jpg image (if"opened" in full page)

metadata.name: Grud #37
metadata.description:
Grud, a speedrun on 31st May 2022. 

The cousin of the BoodMoards, exploring some other shapes, colours and fun ideas. 

Made with p5js. 
23 colour palettes
10 background colours 
11 tile styles 

Big thanks to all collectors and shoutout to the Circolors frens for the support <3 

10% of mint proceeds going to the processing foundation 
42% of royalties to minters. 

Click the image or press 's' or 'S' in live mode to save a 2160 × 2700 png
